    "description": "Go throught the multiple procedurally generated level and defeat the boss. Buy upgrades by collecting enemy gold.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Key Features of version 1.0.0:</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 18 level campaign mode (randomly generated level) <br></li><li> 10+ enemies and 4 different bosses<br></li><li> 3 different playable characters<br></li><li> 30+ unlockable permanent upgrades<br></li><li> 10+ unlockable upgrades for the current run<br></li><li> Steam Achievements</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Starting tips:</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Learn the attacks of the different enemies <br></li><li>Focus on avoiding damage instead of boosting life points<br></li><li>Damage and energy regen are good starting power-ups to spend money on<br></li><li>You can only earn 2 skill-point per level (so don't try to re-run the same level just to grind skill-points)<br></li><li>Don't be too slow as difficulty increase with time</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Roadmap:</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Endless survival mode<br></li><li> New bosses, mini-bosses and enemies<br></li><li> More skills<br></li><li> More buyable upgrades<br></li><li> Weekly challenge with leaderboard<br></li><li> More playable characters<br></li><li> Coop ???</li></ul>",
